==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Relatively
<hw>Rel"a*tive*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a relative manner; in
relation or respect to something else; not absolutely.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Consider the absolute affections of any being as it is in itself,
before you consider it <qex>relatively</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>I.
Watts.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Relativeness</ent>⟦br⟧
